# File & Folder Naming Conventions

## FORBIDDEN File Names

❌ **NEVER create files with these generic names:**

```
page.tsx / Page.tsx
index.tsx / Index.tsx (except for package entry points)
component.tsx / Component.tsx
view.tsx / View.tsx
screen.tsx / Screen.tsx
container.tsx / Container.tsx
```

These names provide zero context about what the file does.

## Required: Descriptive Names

✅ **Every file MUST be named so its purpose is immediately clear:**

| Bad ❌ | Good ✅ |
|--------|---------|
| `page.tsx` | `DashboardView.tsx` |
| `index.tsx` | `UserSettingsForm.tsx` |
| `component.tsx` | `AuthenticationModal.tsx` |
| `Page.tsx` | `TodoListPage.tsx` |
| `view.tsx` | `ApiKeyOverview.tsx` |

## Naming Patterns by Type

### Route Files (`apps/*/src/routes/`)
```
✅ dashboard.tsx
✅ user-settings.tsx
✅ api-keys.tsx
✅ auth/login.tsx
✅ auth/register.tsx

❌ page.tsx
❌ index.tsx (for pages)
```

### Components (`src/components/`)
```
✅ UserMenu.tsx
✅ SignInForm.tsx
✅ ApiKeyCard.tsx
✅ NavigationHeader.tsx

❌ Component.tsx
❌ Card.tsx (too generic unless it's a UI primitive)
```

### UI Primitives (`src/components/ui/`)
```
✅ button.tsx (shadcn convention)
✅ card.tsx
✅ input.tsx
```

### tRPC Routers (`packages/api/src/routers/`)
```
✅ todo.ts
✅ user.ts
✅ api-key.ts
✅ organization.ts

❌ router.ts
❌ index.ts (except for barrel exports)
```

### Utilities & Functions
```
✅ get-user.ts
✅ auth-client.ts
✅ format-date.ts
✅ validate-api-key.ts

❌ utils.ts (exception: single utility file with cn() etc.)
❌ helpers.ts
❌ functions.ts
```

## Folder Structure Rules

### DO: Domain-Based Grouping
```
src/
├── routes/
│   ├── dashboard.tsx
│   ├── auth/
│   │   ├── login.tsx
│   │   └── register.tsx
│   └── settings/
│       ├── profile.tsx
│       └── api-keys.tsx
├── components/
│   ├── auth/
│   │   ├── SignInForm.tsx
│   │   └── SignUpForm.tsx
│   └── dashboard/
│       ├── StatsCard.tsx
│       └── RecentActivity.tsx
```

### DON'T: Folder-Per-File Anti-Pattern
```
❌ src/
    ├── pages/
    │   ├── Dashboard/
    │   │   ├── index.tsx
    │   │   ├── Dashboard.tsx
    │   │   └── Dashboard.module.css
    │   ├── Settings/
    │   │   ├── index.tsx
    │   │   └── Settings.tsx
```

## Allowed `index.ts` Usage

`index.ts` is ONLY allowed for:

1. **Package entry points**: `packages/*/src/index.ts`
2. **Barrel exports**: Re-exporting from a folder
3. **Schema exports**: `packages/db/src/schema/index.ts`

```typescript
// ✅ packages/db/src/schema/index.ts (barrel export)
export * from "./auth";
export * from "./todo";

// ❌ apps/www/src/routes/index.tsx as a page
// Use a descriptive name like home.tsx or landing.tsx instead
```

## Case Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| Route files | kebab-case | `user-settings.tsx` |
| Components | PascalCase | `UserSettings.tsx` |
| Utilities | kebab-case | `format-date.ts` |
| Types/Interfaces | PascalCase | `UserSession.ts` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE | `API_ENDPOINTS.ts` |

## Language

**All file and folder names MUST be in English.**
